ey S, Meeyai A, et al. <span class="ref-title">Strategies for containing an emerging influenza pandemic in Southeast Asia. </span><span class="ref-journal">Nature</span> 2005;<span class="ref-vol">437</span>:209&#x02013;14 10.1038/nature04017 [<a href="/pubmed/16079797" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2666290&amp;issue-id=177893&amp;journal-id=782&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] [<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1038%2Fnature04017" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2666290&amp;issue-id=177893&amp;journal-id=782&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">CrossRef</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Nature&amp;title=Strategies+for+containing+an+emerging+influenza+pandemic+in+Southeast+Asia.&amp;volume=437&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;pages=209-14&amp;pmid=16079797&amp;doi=10.1038/nature04017&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2666290&amp;issue-id=177893&amp;journal-id=782&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="R15">15.  <span class="citation">Chopitayasunondh T, Sawanpanyalert N Clinical practice guideline for human avian influenza (H5N1). Nonthaburi (Thailand): Ministry of Public Health; 2006 <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Chopitayasunondh+++T+,++Sawanpanyalert+++N++Clinical+practice+guideline+for+human+avian+influenza+(H5N1).+Nonthaburi+(Thailand):+Ministry+of+Public+Health;++2006+" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2666290&amp;issue-id=177893&amp;journal-id=782&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="R16">16.  <span class="citation">Chunsuttiwat S, Kanchit L, Darika K, Chariya S, Naruemon S, 